title: I don't get it
text:
I have a subscription where I pay over $20 a month‚Ä¶ There are some basic things that Youtube doesn't do that I just don't understand‚Ä¶

Why can't you rearrange where the to a playlist button is? why can't you ask it to give you more suggestions on your to watch?

Why can't you tell it to give you more of a certain kind of suggestion unless of a different one? I've been on YouTube for years and the past year or so, again even though I'm paying, the recommendations are worse than they used to be!

Why do you have to go through a menu with three different clicks to find your playlist?

Why can't you put your playlists further up in the menu? Rearrange them?

These are such basic intuitive things, I don't understand why they don't catch these things.
